If you're looking for more info on what's
new in Android 4.4 for the Galaxy Note 3,

00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:37.340
make sure you check out parts 1, 2, and 3
in case you've missed it.

00:03:37.340 --> 00:03:41.070
And if you've enjoyed this video, make sure
you hit that like button and subscribe for

00:03:41.070 --> 00:03:42.260
upcoming videos.

